# Migrations

This directory indexes migration and rollout records for `<repo-name>`.

## Belongs Here

- transition plans for documentation structure changes
- cutover notes and rollout checkpoints
- records of how a docs reorganization was carried out

## Does Not Belong Here

- current canonical guidance: `../Architecture/`
- open design alternatives: `../Proposals/`
- durable decision rationale: `../Decisions/`
- retired material that is no longer active: `../Archive/`

## Use

Use this subtree for changeover records while a structure transition is being
carried out or preserved for reference.
